    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "## Problem\n\nCrash after invoking `:!foo` from the ui2 pager.\n\n## Steps to reproduce\n\n```\nnvim --clean --luamod-dev +\"lua require('vim._core.ui2').enable({msg={target='cmd'}})\"\n:!ls\n<Enter>\n:!ls\n<crash>\n```\n\n## Expected behavior\n\nno crash\n\n## System info\n\n- Nvim version (nvim -v): `v0.12.0-dev-2527 gb47b0caba858` neovim/neovim@b47b0caba858\n- Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?: n/a\n- Operating system/version: Darwin 24.6.0\n- Terminal name/version: ghostty 1.3.0\n- $TERM environment variable: `xterm-ghostty`\n- Installation: src\n\n",
